data.description: Discover your dream home in this meticulously maintained ranch home situated in the heart of Portage.  Features an extra large lot that's  fenced in AND a heated 20'x24' Heated Pole Barn/2nd Garage with 15' ceiling and Workshop.  Inside, enjoy a new Quartz kitchen w/ skylights, 3-season room, new baths, fireplace, hardwood floors, new light fixtures & doors, a full finished basement, new patio & retaining wall, a 2-car attached garage. Convenient access to Oakland Drive Park where there is sledding, pickleball/tennis courts, pavilion, volleyball court, & more. Nestled in a vibrant community near schools, shopping, restaurants, trails, & major roads like US 131 & I-94, this home offers an unparalleled level of convenience. Portage Schools further add to the appeal.
